# 📚 Maths The Fun Way

An interactive and user-friendly maths tutorial website designed to make learning enjoyable and effective for students from Year 1 to Year 12.

---

## 🎯 Project Objectives

- ✅ Provide **free maths lessons** for Year 1 to Year 12 students.
- ✅ Offer an **engaging user interface** using only HTML and CSS.
- ✅ Support both **self-paced learning** and **private tutoring options**.
- ✅ Make the website **accessible on laptops, tablets, and smartphones**.
- ✅ Highlight key features like:
  - Teacher availability
  - Money-back guarantee
  - Fun, game-based learning
- ✅ Build a solid structure for future enhancements with JavaScript or backend logic.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🏠 Clean homepage with navigation menu
- 🔍 Simple search box to look up topics
- 🎓 Free lesson links categorized by academic year
- 🤝 Private tutor and sign-up options
- 📱 Fully responsive layout (mobile-friendly)
- ✅ Benefits section to build user trust

---

## 💻 Technologies Used

- **HTML5** – for structure
- **CSS3** – for styling and layout
- *(No JavaScript or backend used in this version)*

---



